lyrics:
[Verse]
On the road to hell, it's said to be paved with gold
With good intentions, my story must be told
I swear, I believed I was heading for the sky
Building a castle, where dreams would never die

[Chorus]
But it all came crashing down, oh, so suddenly
In the blink of an eye, shattered my reverie
The road to hell was paved in disguise, you see
My beautiful dream ripped apart, just like me
